This simulation models the day to day activities of the patient, her daughter and her caregiver as reported in the interview.
For this simulation equilibrium difficulties have been modeled. Each and every time the patient tries to get out of bed or up from a chair she falls and asks for help.
This simulation mimicks the patients mobility problems. A filter is applied to every walking the agent does so it becomes twice as slow as she would do it normally.

This simulation combines both filters created for this model. On one hand, the patient is twice as slow while walking and on the other one she loses her equilibrium and falls every time shw raises from bed of sits up from a chair without help.
